      <title>ICPC寒假刷题NO. 1    踩坑日记</title>
      <link href="/2020/01/31/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83NO.1/%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2020/01/31/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83NO.1/%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[        <h2   id="S-平方和与立方和" >          <span class="heading-link">S - 平方和与立方和</span>        </h2>      <p><img src="/pictures/ACM寒假训练/训练一_题目S.png" alt="题目"><br>题目给定了一段连续的整数，也就是说给定了两个端点为 n, m 的一段区间。题目并不难，但是有一个坑</p><p><strong>错误代码</strong></p><ul><li>  <figure class="highlight c"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> n, m;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> sum_odd = <span class="number">0</span>, sum_even = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = n; i &lt;= m; i++)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(i % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            sum_even += i * i;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">            sum_odd += i * i * i;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; sum_even &lt;&lt; <span class="string">" "</span> &lt;&lt; sum_odd &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><strong>错因</strong></li><li>人家只说了端点是 n, m ，又没说哪一个是左端点，哪一个是右端点</li></ul><p><strong>正确解法</strong></p><ul><li>对 n, m 的大小做一个判断，确保 n 是左端点，m 是右端点  <figure class="highlight c"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> n, m;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n &gt; m)</span><br><span class="line">        swap(n, m);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> sum_odd = <span class="number">0</span>, sum_even = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = n; i &lt;= m; i++)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(i % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            sum_even += i * i;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">            sum_odd += i * i * i;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; sum_even &lt;&lt; <span class="string">" "</span> &lt;&lt; sum_odd &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
