      <title>ICPC寒假刷题NO. 1    代码写法的问题</title>
      <link href="/2020/01/31/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83NO.1/%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2020/01/31/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83NO.1/%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[        <h2   id="F-A-B-for-Input-Output-Practice-III" >          <span class="heading-link">F - A+B for Input-Output Practice (III)</span>        </h2>      <p><img src="/pictures/ACM寒假训练/训练一_题目F.png" alt="题目"><br>题目很简单，但是出错的地方值得记录</p><p><strong>错误代码</strong></p><ul><li>  <figure class="highlight c"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> a, b;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(a == b == <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">long</span> sum = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    sum = a + b;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; sum &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><strong>错因</strong></li><li><code>a == b == 0</code> 当 a = b 时，a == b 的值是 1 ，!= 0，不会进 if<br>  当 a != b 时，a == b 的值是 0 ，反而会进 if<br><strong>正确解法</strong></li><li>用另一种表现形式  <figure class="highlight c"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(!a &amp;&amp; !b)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
