      <title>ICPC寒假刷题NO. 1    小技巧</title>
      <link href="/2020/01/27/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83NO.1/%E5%B0%8F%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/"/>
      <url>/2020/01/27/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83/ICPC%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83NO.1/%E5%B0%8F%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><p><span class="external-link"><a   href="https://vjudge.net/contest/353848#problem/A"  target="_blank" rel="noopener">A - A + B Problem</a><i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span><br>ACM的题目常常会有<strong>多组数据</strong>，最后结束会以<span class="external-link"><a   href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/EOF/1017800?fr=aladdin"  target="_blank" rel="noopener">EOF</a><i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>结束。这道题自己的<strong>问题在于不知道怎么用cpp去读EOF</strong></p><p>  如果用C语言，可以这么写：</p>  <figure class="highlight cpp"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d"</span>, &amp;a, &amp;b) != EOF)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>  <strong>而cpp这样写即可</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight cpp"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></li></ul><ul><li><p><span class="external-link"><a   href="https://vjudge.net/contest/353848#problem/N"  target="_blank" rel="noopener">N - 计算球体积</a><i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span><br>  对于π的计算</p>  <figure class="highlight c"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">double</span> PI = <span class="built_in">acos</span>(<span class="number">-1.0</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>  这是<strong>非常标准并且正确</strong>的<br>  但是在这道题中，题目已经给出了π的值，这种情况下应该用题目给的值</p></li><li><p>怎么用cpp实现对小数点位数的控制<br>  一些题目会对保留几位小数有要求。<br>  以保留两位为例</p><p>  c语言</p>  <figure class="highlight cpp"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%.2lf"</span>, a);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>  cpp<br>  首先要</p>  <figure class="highlight cpp"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iomanip&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>  然后</p>  <figure class="highlight cpp"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; fixed &lt;&lt; setprecision(<span class="number">2</span>) &lt;&lt; distance &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>  <strong>fixed表示位数不够会补0<br>  setprecision(位数)</strong></p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
